# 1. Project Overview

This project implements a **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot** using the **Gemma3 LLM**, running locally via Ollama.

Unlike basic RAG systems, this implementation includes:
- Custom context retrieval logic
- Manual prompt engineering
- Automated evaluation using AI-as-Judge
- Real-time hallucination and confidence scoring
- Fault-tolerant system with auto-recovery

The chatbot can answer questions using both:
- Knowledge Base (URLs + PDF)
- General model knowledge

