# 6. Evaluation System

Each response is evaluated automatically using **Agent-as-Judge**.

## Metrics

### 1. Hallucination Score
- Detects fabricated information
- Scale: 0-10
- Formula:
  ```
  Hallucination = 1 - (Score / 10)
  ```

### 2. Confidence Score
- Measures clarity and certainty
- Scale: 0-10
- Formula:
  ```
  Confidence = Score / 10
  ```

---

## Score Interpretation

| Score | Hallucination Risk | Confidence | Status |
|------|------------------|-----------|--------|
| 8-10 | Low | High | PASS |
| 7 | Moderate | Moderate | PASS |
| 4-6 | High | Medium | FAIL |
| 0-3 | Very High | Low | FAIL |

